         </origination>
    
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_0af0df050e271d203237eb31b40bad87">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>In 1959 Dr. Ba Maw donated these papers to Yale University. In December 1965 he transferred them to the Burmese government; the collection now in Manuscripts and Archives is made up entirely of photostatic copies of the originals.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_56a6c6db4fe73f456feef26438247461">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_db2f5e66cf5a44c7dab74dfbb1a5bc4c">
